query:
SELECT LOWER(symptom) as symptom_lower, COUNT(DISTINCT symptom) as variations, GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT symptom SEPARATOR ' | ') as all_variations
FROM defects
GROUP BY LOWER(symptom)
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT symptom) > 1;
